# Deploy outputs at repo root — generated by deploy.sh from core/ when
# this repo is used as a deploy target during local testing.
# Source templates live in core/; root-level deploy outputs must never be
# committed. The repo-specific AGENTS.md at the root IS tracked — it
# documents how to maintain this template library and is unrelated to the
# AGENTS.md that deploy.sh writes into target repos.
